::  Allows one ship to ping another with a string of text
::
::::  /===/app/ping/hoon
  ::
/-  ping-message
::
!:
|%
+=  move  [bone card]
+=  card  $%  [%poke wire dock poke-contents]
          ==
+=  poke-contents  $%  [%atom @]
                   ==
--
|_  [bow=bowl:gall ~]                                        ::<  stateless
::
++  poke-ping-message
  |=  ping-message
  ~&  ping+'Message sent!'
  ^-  [(list move) _+>.$]
  :_  +>.$
  :_  ~
  [ost.bow %poke /sending [to dap.bow] %atom message]
::
++  poke-atom
  |=  arg=@
  ~&  ping+'Message received!'
  ^-  [(list move) _+>.$]
  ~&  ping+message+(@t arg)
  [~ +>.$]
::
++  coup  |=(* `+>)
--
